Determines whether or not word token are automatically lowercased. If the flag argument is <code>true</code>, then the value in the <code>sval</code> field is lowercased whenever a word token is returned (the <code>ttype</code> field has the value <code>TT_WORD</code> by the <code>nextToken</code> method of this tokenizer. <p> If the flag argument is <code>false</code>, then the <code>sval</code> field is not modified.
